    section#about.aboutus.white-background.black
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-12.text-center.black
            h3.title
              | ABOUT 
              span.themecolor US
            p.a-slog
              | Arvin Simbulan Photography is one of the leading, fast-rising companies in Digital Photo and Video Services. Consistently in the TOPS bookers in Wedding Expo Philippines and Philippine Wedding Summit, biggest bridal fair in the country organized by Themes & Motifs, we give only the best quality and value-for money services.
              

        .gap
        .row.about-box
          .col-sm-4.text-center
            .margin-bottom
              i.fa.fa-newspaper-o
              h4 CREATIVITY
              p.black
                | We are committed to a culture of creativity. This comes in many forms such as in the portraits that we make and products we come up with which allows us to be ahead of our competitors. We are proud to share and build on the artistic talents of our colleagues and be able to provide them a venue to be creative.
            // / margin
          // /col
          .col-sm-4.about-line.text-center
            .margin-bottom
              i.fa.fa-diamond
